io.github.utk003.util.math

Class Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.utk003.util.math.Constants

  • @ScheduledForRelease(inVersion="v3.0.0")
public abstract class Constants
extends Object
    A collection of useful math constants to very high precision.

    Most of these constants are not provided by Math, and the few that are are given to lower precision. Every constant provided by this class is accurate to the 24th decimal place (ie rounded to the nearest 10-24).

    Since:
    3.0.0
    Version:
    July 20, 2021
    Author:
    Utkarsh Priyam (utk003)
